OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779872685
OL,3,CEd Sheeran beats Taylor Swift as the
OL,4,CUK's most played artist in 2025
OL,6,FBritish singer-songwriter Ed Sheeran
OL,7,Fhas beaten Taylor Swift as the UK's
OL,8,Fmost played artist of 2025, according
OL,9,Fto music licensing agency Phonographic
OL,10,FPerformance Limited (PPL).
OL,12,FThe 35-year-old topped PPL's charts
OL,13,Facross radio, TV and public places,
OL,14,Fwith his music played an average of
OL,15,F574 times per day, equating to 24
OL,16,Fplays per hour.
OL,18,FIt is Sheeran's eighth time topping
OL,19,Fthe charts in 11 years, with Taylor
OL,20,FSwift coming in second place, followed
OL,21,Fby Dua Lipa in third place.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
