PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779872685
OL,3,CEd Sheeran beats Taylor Swift as the
OL,4,CUK's most played artist in 2025
OL,6,FThe singer said: "I am so grateful to
OL,7,Fbe named most-played artist across TV,
OL,8,Fradio and venues across the UK for an
OL,9,Fincredible eighth time.
OL,11,F"A huge thanks to everyone who has
OL,12,Fplayed my music over the last year,
OL,13,Fand over the last 15 years. I really
OL,14,Fappreciate the continuing support."
OL,16,FThe rest of the top 10 included Calvin
OL,17,FHarris, Ariana Grande and Sir Elton
OL,18,FJohn.
OL,20,FThe full list of the most played
OL,21,Fartists in 2025, according to PPL:
OL,26,@nD@ROUsD@AOUvD@cO]
