OL,3,CEd Sheeran beats Taylor Swift as the
OL,4,CUK's most played artist in 2025
OL,6,F9. Sabrina Carpenter
OL,8,F10. Lady Gaga
OL,10,FBritish singer-songwriter Myles Smith
OL,11,Fhad PPL's most-played track of the
OL,12,Fyear with Nice To Meet You.
OL,14,FLola Young's Messy came in second,
OL,15,FAlex Warren's Ordinary in third and
OL,16,FSam Fender's People Watching in fourth.
