OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779872685
OL,3,CEd Sheeran beats Taylor Swift as the
OL,4,CUK's most played artist in 2025
OL,6,FSmith said: "Having the most-played
OL,7,Fsong in the UK last year with Nice To
OL,8,FMeet You and seeing Stargazing still
OL,9,Fin the top 10 - honestly, it still
OL,10,Fdoesn't feel real.
OL,12,F"I'm so grateful to everyone who has
OL,13,Flistened, to my fans who have been
OL,14,Fwith me from the beginning and to
OL,15,Feveryone at radio and in the venues
OL,16,Fwho has supported the music. It means
OL,17,Feverything."
OL,19,FThe full list of most played songs in
OL,20,F2025, according to PPL:
